==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Leaved
<hw>Leaved</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Leaf</er>.]</ety> <def>Bearing, or having, a leaf or leaves; having
folds; -- used in combination; <as>as, a four<ex>-leaved</ex> clover; a
two-<ex>leaved</ex> gate; long<ex>-leaved</ex>.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Leaveless</ent>⟦br⟧
